findLastAlignedEntry

public static int findLastAlignedEntry(java.util.List<CRAIEntry> list)
Find index of the last aligned entry in the list. Assumes the index is sorted by coordinate and unmapped entries (with sequence id = -1) follow the mapped entries.

Parameters:
list - a list of CRAI entries
Returns:
integer index of the last entry with sequence id not equal to -1
